    {
      "id": "doc000-chunk000",
      "source": "examples\\sample_docs\\company_handbook.txt",
      "text": "AI Product Team Handbook\n\nThe team builds internal AI tools for knowledge search, customer support, and document question answering.\n\nEvery answer generated by an AI assistant should include citations when the answer depends on internal documents.\n\nBefore shipping an LLM feature, the team evaluates retrieval quality, answer faithfulness, latency, cost, and failure cases.\n\nFor sensitive or high-risk domains, the assistant should say when context is missing instead of guessing.\n\n团队要求所有知识库问答功能都要保留引用来源。没有足够上下文时，系统应该提示上下文不足，而不是编造答案。",
      "start_char": 0,
      "end_char": 533,
      "metadata": {
        "name": "company_handbook.txt",
        "extension": ".txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "doc001-chunk000",
      "source": "examples\\sample_docs\\nlp_job_notes.md",
      "text": "# NLP And LLM Engineer Notes\n\nAn NLP or LLM application engineer should understand tokenization, embeddings, vector search, prompt design, retrieval augmented generation, evaluation, Python packaging, tests, and deployment.\n\nFor interviews, it is useful to explain tradeoffs. Chunk size changes retrieval behavior. Embedding model choice changes semantic recall. Reranking can improve precision. Evaluation should include retrieval quality and answer faithfulness.\n\n中文求职准备可以围绕五个能力展开：Python 工程能力、NLP 基础、RAG 应用开发、评估方法、部署和监控。\n\n一个好的作品集项目应该能运行、能解释、有测试、有 README、有示例数据，并且能清楚说明它解决了什么真实问题。",
      "start_char": 0,
      "end_char": 580,
      "metadata": {
        "name": "nlp_job_notes.md",
        "extension": ".md"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "doc002-chunk000",
      "source": "examples\\sample_docs\\rag_notes.md",
      "text": "# RAG Doctor Notes\n\nRAG Doctor evaluates retrieval augmented generation pipelines. It checks whether the retriever found relevant chunks, whether the answer is grounded in citations, and whether the result has hallucination risk.\n\nThe first version uses a simple hashing embedder. This makes the project easy to run without external services. Later versions can replace the embedder with bge, sentence-transformers, OpenAI embeddings, FAISS, or Chroma.\n\nGood RAG systems need reliable document loading, careful chunking, useful embeddings, strong retrieval, citation-aware answers, and repeatable evaluation.\n\nRAG Doctor 可以帮助定位 RAG 应用为什么答错，例如检索没有命中、上下文太弱、答案没有引用、或者存在幻觉风险。",
      "start_char": 0,
      "end_char": 671,
      "metadata": {
        "name": "rag_notes.md",
        "extension": ".md"
      }
    }
  ],
